summary: Changes your cursor to Navi, from Zelda!
descriptionHtml:
Animated Navi cursor, animated and leaves a trail of fairy dust! Bawwwww! Oh and best of all, never says \"HEY LISTEN!\".

- Compatible with Nexus Mod Manager

## Installation ##

Place \'cursormenu.swf\' in [Skyrim installation folder]/Data/Interface

## Uninstallation ##

Remove \'cursormenu.swf\' from [Skyrim installation folder]/Data/Interface

---

Enjoy :)

Mod by:
Kenney Vleugels
www.kenney.nl
